ows-buy-tickets-3497458">罗德里戈的 2024 年“胆量”世界巡演</a>目前预计将持续到 8 月中旬，在今年晚些时候在英国、爱尔兰和欧洲停留之前，还将在北美举办更多巡演。英国站的特色是在伦敦 O2 体育馆住四晚。</p><p>您可以在此处（英国/爱尔兰）和<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/olivia-rodrigo-tickets/artist/2836194?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=QHQVEUQchxyPR5sWCQS0k2gbUkH16I1%3AiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>（北美） <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/olivia-rodrigo-tickets/artist/5367175?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkH16Iw2iX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">找到任何剩余门票</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-olivia-rodrigo-bring-out-noah-kahan-for-stick-season-in-new-york-3614400">《观看奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo) 与诺亚·卡汉 (Noah Kahan) 在纽约出演《Stick Season》》</a>的帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
